Our last resort is

269
00:17:46,344 --> 00:17:49,604
[ Pulse therapy: High dosage of steroids ]
administering a high dosage pulse therapy.

270
00:17:49,604 --> 00:17:52,144
If your immune system
weakens more...

271
00:17:52,144 --> 00:17:54,474
your body couldn't handle it.

272
00:17:59,294 --> 00:18:02,164
What is the reason you're
gathered here today?

273
00:18:02,164 --> 00:18:03,674
We heard the news that

274
00:18:03,674 --> 00:18:06,294
Hansae Hospital excluded
a genuine and skilled doctor

275
00:18:06,294 --> 00:18:07,834
from treatments because

276
00:18:07,834 --> 00:18:10,024
he's suffering from CIPA disease.

277
00:18:10,024 --> 00:18:12,074
This skilled doctor
whom you speak of.

278
00:18:12,074 --> 00:18:13,984
Is he Dr. Cha Yo Han

279
00:18:13,984 --> 00:18:15,954
who diagnosed your
ailment previously?

280
00:18:15,954 --> 00:18:17,334
Yes.

281
00:18:17,334 --> 00:18:21,624
He is a crucial presence
for the patients.

282
00:18:21,624 --> 00:18:23,424
We're here to

283
00:18:23,424 --> 00:18:26,164
deliver the message to the
hospital not only from myself,

284
00:18:26,164 --> 00:18:28,464
but many who agree.

285
00:18:28,464 --> 00:18:30,584
What an effort.

286
00:18:30,584 --> 00:18:33,004
I went from hospital to hospital,

287
00:18:33,004 --> 00:18:35,834
and my pain worsened
without knowing the cause.

288
00:18:35,834 --> 00:18:37,544
- The doctors and my family...
- Yes?

289
00:18:37,544 --> 00:18:38,984
Hello, Dr. Cha?

290
00:18:38,984 --> 00:18:40,814
Ki Seok won't open his eyes.

291
00:18:40,814 --> 00:18:42,744
His pupillary reflex is slow, too.

292
00:18:42,744 --> 00:18:44,884
His vitals were stable so
we stopped the medication,

293
00:18:44,884 --> 00:18:46,114
but he developed bradycardia.

294
00:18:46,114 --> 00:18:47,824
His blood pressure
keeps rising, it's 160...

295
00:18:47,824 --> 00:18:48,804
What's the relaxation phase?

296
00:18:48,804 --> 00:18:49,984
It's 76.

297
00:18:49,984 --> 00:18:51,264
I think his brain pressure is rising.

298
00:18:51,264 --> 00:18:54,034
Raise his breathing for now
and administer mannitol.

299
00:18:54,034 --> 00:18:56,094
I'll head over right now.

300
00:19:01,454 --> 00:19:03,474
[ Gyeongseo University Hospital ]

301
00:19:08,304 --> 00:19:10,234
Hansae Hospital, please.

302
00:19:38,304 --> 00:19:39,694
Yes, Dr. Cha.

303
00:19:39,694 --> 00:19:41,214
How is Ki Seok?

304
00:19:41,214 --> 00:19:43,514
He has pupil full dilatation.

305
00:19:43,534 --> 00:19:45,034
[ Pupil full dilatation: Blown pupil,
a symptom of pressure inside the skull ]

306
00:19:45,054 --> 00:19:47,454
If we don't remove the abscess,
his brain will be damaged.

307
00:19:47,454 --> 00:19:50,204
Consult with Neurosurgery Dept.
and arrange for an OR.

308
00:19:50,204 --> 00:19:51,434
And...

309
00:19:52,744 --> 00:19:54,354
get his guardian's consent.

310
00:20:00,304 --> 00:20:03,954
We can insert a tube to remove the
abscess and reduce the pressure.

311
00:20:03,954 --> 00:20:06,154
But the pus spread
throughout the brain,

312
00:20:06,154 --> 00:20:07,954
so we can't remove all of it.

313
00:20:07,954 --> 00:20:10,424
The brain stem especially
is too risky.

314
00:20:10,424 --> 00:20:13,764
We can't guarantee his brain will
function normally after the surgery.

315
00:20:13,764 --> 00:20:16,704
As you know, we can't control the
pressure with just medication.

316
00:20:16,704 --> 00:20:18,994
We have no other option but surgery.

317
00:20:25,194 --> 00:20:26,684
If he gets surgery...

318
00:20:28,174 --> 00:20:29,384
will he recover?

319
00:20:30,544 --> 00:20:33,664
As he has serious
neurological symptoms,

320
00:20:33,664 --> 00:20:35,304
we can't guarantee

321
00:20:35,304 --> 00:20:38,224
whether Ki Seok will return to his

322
00:20:38,224 --> 00:20:40,704
original state after surgery.

323
00:20:40,704 --> 00:20:43,794
However, if we don't operate now,

324
00:20:43,794 --> 00:20:46,044
he may become brain dead.

325
00:21:01,754 --> 00:21:05,644
The surgery requested by
Anesthesiology is meaningless.

326
00:21:10,834 --> 00:21:12,034
Hello.

327
00:21:14,734 --> 00:21:16,034
[ Current Operation Room Status ]

328
00:21:17,744 --> 00:21:19,984
- Dr. Cha.
- Why isn't the OR ready?

329
00:21:19,984 --> 00:21:21,484
We just received a call.

330
00:21:21,484 --> 00:21:23,244
They're still talking to the OR...

331
00:21:28,024 --> 00:21:30,514
Ma'am, you signed the
consent form, correct?

332
00:21:30,514 --> 00:21:31,234
Yes.

333
00:21:31,234 --> 00:21:32,914
We'll operate on Ki Seok right now.

334
00:21:34,994 --> 00:21:37,644
- What are you doing? Move him now.
- Dr. Cha.

335
00:21:37,644 --> 00:21:39,614
As you know,
the placement is bad.

336
00:21:39,614 --> 00:21:41,354
You must rationally think over

337
00:21:41,434 --> 00:21:43,434
how dangerous this is
for Ki Seok, and

338
00:21:43,434 --> 00:21:45,734
- what his chances of recovery are.
- Dangerous?

339
00:21:45,734 --> 00:21:47,754
If we don't, he'll die.
What can be worse?

340
00:21:50,224 --> 00:21:51,494
Switch to an Ambu.

341
00:21:57,384 --> 00:21:58,914
What are you doing?

342
00:21:58,914 --> 00:22:01,504
His brain pressure is rising rapidly
and causing neuro damage.

343
00:22:01,504 --> 00:22:03,174
We must operate
before he's brain dead.

344
00:22:03,174 --> 00:22:04,324
I saw his chart.

345
00:22:04,324 --> 00:22:06,694
You know his chances of
recovery are low regardless.

346
00:22:06,694 --> 00:22:09,154
If we don't, his chances of
recovery won't be low.

347
00:22:09,154 --> 00:22:10,454
He won't be recovering at all.

348
00:22:10,454 --> 00:22:13,694
But this is "recovery" won't
restore him to his old self.

349
00:22:13,694 --> 00:22:14,734
Worst case scenario,

350
00:22:14,734 --> 00:22:17,294
he may spend the rest
of his life in that state.

351
00:22:18,404 --> 00:22:19,634
Is the Ambu ready?

352
00:22:20,834 --> 00:22:22,434
- Move aside.
- Dr. Cha.

353
00:22:22,434 --> 00:22:24,334
I said move. If we don't,
this patient will die!

354
00:22:24,334 --> 00:22:26,734
You could be inflicting
even more pain!

355
00:22:36,974 --> 00:22:39,394
Are you really doing
this for the patient?

356
00:22:41,814 --> 00:22:43,264
As a doctor,

357
00:22:43,264 --> 00:22:46,044
is this in accordance with
the decisions you've made

358
00:22:46,044 --> 00:22:47,594
thus far?

359
00:22:52,934 --> 00:22:54,134
Please step aside.

360
00:22:55,134 --> 00:22:57,234
His guardian consented
to the surgery.

361
00:22:58,334 --> 00:22:59,434
Move.

362
00:23:02,734 --> 00:23:04,334
Ki Seok.

363
00:23:05,134 --> 00:23:06,334
Ki Seok...

364
00:23:08,434 --> 00:23:09,714
He has bradycardia.

365
00:23:09,714 --> 00:23:11,244
His blood pressure is 65 over 20.

366
00:23:11,244 --> 00:23:12,544
The SpO2 is 80.

367
00:23:12,544 --> 00:23:14,134
Administer one ampule of atropine.

368
00:23:16,134 --> 00:23:17,194
Ki Seok...

369
00:23:19,994 --> 00:23:21,564
No response. Epinephrine.

370
00:23:28,034 --> 00:23:29,134
Ki Seok.

371
00:23:36,514 --> 00:23:38,314
Ma'am, please stay here.

372
00:23:38,314 --> 00:23:39,574
Just for a little while.

373
00:23:39,574 --> 00:23:41,044
Go inside!

374
00:23:42,174 --> 00:23:43,774
[ Restricted Area ]

375
00:23:43,774 --> 00:23:45,534
Ki Seok...

376
00:23:57,364 --> 00:23:58,684
I'll do it.

377
00:24:12,834 --> 00:24:14,834
Dr. Cha, I'll take over.

378
00:24:24,334 --> 00:24:26,734
Ki Seok's guardian is asking for you.

379
00:24:55,114 --> 00:24:56,684
Dr. Kang.

380
00:25:03,914 --> 00:25:05,394
Live.

381
00:25:07,384 --> 00:25:08,884
You must live, Ki Seok.

382
00:25:10,024 --> 00:25:11,384
Please live.

383
00:25:13,294 --> 00:25:14,444
Ki Seok.

384
00:25:27,304 --> 00:25:28,984
- Please live...
- Dr. Cha.

385
00:25:30,084 --> 00:25:31,674
Please stop.

386
00:25:33,154 --> 00:25:36,094
Ki Seok's mother says
she wants to stop.

387
00:25:40,584 --> 00:25:42,674
She doesn't want him to
have surgery, either.

388
00:25:42,674 --> 00:25:44,194
Ki Seok.

389
00:25:44,194 --> 00:25:47,294
Please live, you must live.

390
00:25:55,284 --> 00:25:56,624
Ki Seok.

391
00:25:57,884 --> 00:25:59,374
Stay strong.

392
00:26:01,384 --> 00:26:04,204
Stay strong, so the
next time we meet,

393
00:26:04,204 --> 00:26:06,414
you'll be your healthy self.

394
00:26:06,414 --> 00:26:10,804
The same disease as me?

395
00:26:12,004 --> 00:26:14,704
- Like you, Dr. Cha.
- Yes.

396
00:26:14,734 --> 00:26:16,234
Like me.

397
00:26:49,334 --> 00:26:52,134
Please let Ki Seok go in peace.

398
00:26:59,334 --> 00:27:01,734
[ Don't get sick without
my permission ]

