405
00:28:15,804 --> 00:28:17,144
Yes?

406
00:28:18,384 --> 00:28:21,584
- Why don't you confirm with him?
- But why?

407
00:28:21,584 --> 00:28:23,634
He's not going to stay
at our hospital.

408
00:28:23,634 --> 00:28:24,924
Unni!

409
00:28:24,924 --> 00:28:26,634
Unni, get up.

410
00:28:26,634 --> 00:28:28,054
Why would I go there?

411
00:28:28,054 --> 00:28:29,784
You may regret it later.

412
00:28:29,784 --> 00:28:30,904
I'm sorry.

